  <title> Configuring <app>Accerciser</app></title>
  <p>
    Some elements in <app>Accerciser</app> are configurable: plugins, global hotkeys, and widget's highlighting.
    To reconfigure any of these elements, do either <key>ctrl</key>+<key>p</key> or <guiseq><gui>Edit</gui>
    <gui>Preferences</gui></guiseq> to open a dialog filled with configurations for them.
  </p>

